      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 1 Business Day article about purchase of National Computer Systems Inc by Pearson PLC</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Tuesday about the purchase of National Computer Systems Inc. by Pearson P.L.C. misstated Pearson's relationship to Simon &amp; Schuster. Pearson acquired Simon &amp; Schuster's educational publishing operation in 1998; Viacom owns the Simon &amp; Schuster trade publishing operation and the name.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
